"(\"Create and Edit text objects\"), but it does not appear on my interactive "
"image. Why?}\\\\ $\\rightarrow$ Unless you make a bitmap copy of the text, "
"Xia will consider the text created with the \"Create and Edit text Objects\" "
"as a detail, and not an image."
